Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:53.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,My dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:56.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Year 1, Class 1, Kamogawa Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:02:01.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,My dream is to become a rocket driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:06.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,That's because I've heard that the Earth is very\Npretty when you look at it from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:11.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,So I want to become a rocket driver and go into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:15.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I want to take people to all sorts of different planets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:19.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,And when they're on my rocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:23.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,my dad and Lion-san will get special free rides!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:26.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:32.19,Spica - Title,,0,0,90,,Even Underwater, There Is Space
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:42.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'm here at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:45.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,This is my dream, the world of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:46.54,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Oumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:53.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,A24-21, Oumi Kei-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:55.09,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:59.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Were you taking a nap standing up or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:02.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,N-No, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:08.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:10.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What's up with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:15.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Now, type in your number using this keyboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:20.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Good, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:21.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Next person!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:27.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,A24-22, Kamogawa Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:31.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Are they even going to have a space suit that fits a 143 cm tall dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.91,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,What are you so depressed about, Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:15.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Today was just a size fitting, so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:19.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The underwater zero-gravity exercise is later, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,That's right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:24.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Don't worry about it! They're special-ordering\None for you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:27.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,We're just getting hand-me-downs from the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:32.27,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Don't just brood over it forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,But, those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:41.65,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Even now, when I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:49.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,How long are you guys gonna keep laughing about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:52.62,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Sorry sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:56.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,eat a lot of different things...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:56.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Instead of always eating rice balls
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:59.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,...and get bigger by the time you go to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:03.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,But I think it could be safer to be small.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:04.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:07.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,When you actually perform an EVA...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:13.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,it's better to slightly lower the chances\Nof hitting meteoroids or debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:14.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:18.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Huh? What's a mete... metero-something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:21.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Meteoroids and debris, Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:31.66,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,objects in the void of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:31.66,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Meteoroids are very small celestial
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:33.70,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,which sometimes become meteorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:40.58,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,And debris is what you call the trash-like stuff that people leave behind in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:43.80,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Starting with Sputnik which launched in 1957...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:46.88,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,the upper half of the rockets used for launching satellites...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:52.64,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,used-up satellites, broken pieces, paint fragments...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.10,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,even gloves dropped by astronauts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:58.19,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Large amounts of garbage are floating in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:02.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I see. There are garbage problems even in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:08.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I can understand meteorites being dangerous\Nbut what's so dangerous about debris?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:13.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Debris flies around in all different directions\Naround the Earth at high speeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:18.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,If you get hit by this debris during an EVA...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:20.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,If you get hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:22.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:25.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Cut it out, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:29.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Well, it just goes to show that there are all sorts\Nof dangers if we make it out into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:33.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Huh? What are we supposed to\Ndo it something happens, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:37.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Asumi, don't ever leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:43.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Moron, it's space. We won't have\Ntime to be looking after others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:45.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I won't be asking you for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:51.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Well, if the time comes, well probably\Nonly protect our highest priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:07:01.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,But I hope I won't run away from those I have to\Nprotect because of my fears and weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:10.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,So even impudent guys like you have their fears, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:11.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:13.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,My eyebrows, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:17.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Is that why you shaved them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:19.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,How would that be the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:40.08,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Geez, we won't get to class on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:56.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I don't really like exercise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:08:00.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,but whenever I hear the word "pool"\Nsomehow I always get excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:06.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,If we weren't wearing this, it would be the best...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.90,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Hey Kei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:12.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Can you pull up the zipper on the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:13.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Your back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:16.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What are you doing, Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You put it on backward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,We're gonna be late, Asumi! Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:24.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:31.63,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,How unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:38.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You're always smiling so much that it's sickening.\Nno matter what class you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:40.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:43.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'm the same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:54.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,meters wearing a flight suit and shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:54.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,For this training lesson, you will swim one hundred
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:59.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Think of yourself as the only one you can depend on in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:03.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,No matter what happens, don't trouble your teammates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:08.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Keep in mind that this is training for\Nsuch a situation, so do it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:09.34,Spica - Secondary,,0,0,90,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:12.17,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Damn that devil instructor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:17.09,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,because my form was a little off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:17.09,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,He didn't have to work me so hard just
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:19.80,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,If it's for your safety it's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:24.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'd rather you train more,\Ninstead of complaining so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:27.19,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Hey just what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:31.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It means that I'd never want to go into space with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:33.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:36.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'd rather die than go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:42.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,If anything happens Asumi will be there to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:49.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Kamogawa-san, if you don't stop being\Nnice you'll eventually lose your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:54.13,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Sacrificing yourself for someone else is foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:10:00.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,to save a twisted person like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:10:00.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'll tell you there's no one who'd want
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:00.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:04.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I can protect myself on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It really is irritating watching all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:09.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Marika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:12.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I can understand what you're saying, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:17.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,But, you can't go to space alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:25.74,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,intoxicated with just getting in this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:25.74,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,I don't want to be told that by someone who s
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:28.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'm not intoxicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:37.30,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Ukita Marika, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:38.26,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,I've heard of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:43.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You sure know a lot when it comes to girls, you playboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Well, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What's a playboy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:49.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You don't need to know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:54.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,To tell you the truth, her father and\Nmy grandfather know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:59.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I've only heard her name before, but\NI didn't think we'd be classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:03.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I thought she was far older.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:09.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The one donating the most to this\Nschool is her father, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:13.00,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Wow, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:15.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Big deal, it's just a little donation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:16.88,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:19.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,But it was hundreds of millions of yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:21.34,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Hundreds of millions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:55.96,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,You can't go to space alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.89,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,You alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.89,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Hey hey girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:07.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Wanna go karaoke together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:12.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's all right! C'mon, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:13.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:16.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Stop putting on airs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:20.23,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Hey you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:24.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,If you rough up a girl, I'll call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:28.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What the hell? We just asked her out for karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:29.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:32.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Huh? Aren't you a Space School student?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:39.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,because you were worried about Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:39.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You came to the dorm the day of the entrance ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:43.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What are you doing at a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:46.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,to be done with her part-time Job?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:46.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Ah, could you be waiting for Asumi-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:51.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,See, over there? There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:58.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,be a little longer before she gets out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:58.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,She always works real late so I think it ll
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.19,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Are you ready to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:02.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's amazing that she can continue to work on top of school...
Comment: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:19.15,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.88,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Ah, I give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:25.13,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,What's wrong, Ooyama-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:29.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I special ordered a space suit for a\Nstudent that couldn't fit into one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:32.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It seems like it will cost more money than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:38.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The government official's purse strings\Nare tight, so there's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:40.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,If that's it, it's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:48.95,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Well, let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:51.37,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,I still have something to do, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:53.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Huh? You have work today, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:56.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Um, no, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.04,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:00.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'll go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Yeah, see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:36.00,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,I hope I won't run away from those I have to protect because of my fears and weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:40.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I wonder if I can do it as well, Lion-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:14:58.93,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Worried about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:05.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,but the truth is she's scared of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:05.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Kamogawa's swimming like that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:13.20,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,When she was small, she almost drowned in a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:16.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I think she's still pretty scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,...so I'm not sure what's gotten in to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:30.38,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,She's a stupid dummy that doesn't have any\Ncommon sense, and that can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,But don't bully her so much, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:36.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,it's not like I was bullying...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:11.55,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,That dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:15.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Trying so hard when she can't swim that well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:21.31,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,That is all for next month's budget distribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:22.77,Spica - Signs,,0,0,90,,Space Astronaut Training Course
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:21.06,Spica - Signs,,0,0,90,,Space Astronaut
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:21.73,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Staff Meeting\NThat is all for next month's budget distribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:23.73,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,That is all for next month's budget distribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:22.77,Spica - Signs,,0,0,90,,Staff Meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:34.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,If you would kindly accept and cooperate...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:35.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:37.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:42.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,this unpleasantly high expense?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:42.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Wait, Ooyama-sensei, what is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:47.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,suit that I mentioned before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:47.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,it is the price of the additional space
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:48.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Additional?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:52.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Kamogawa Asumi, Mr. Principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:52.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,This is about the student named
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,About the size being wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:58.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Ah... but this expense for just one student...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:01.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Isn't there some way to cut the cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:06.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It is a suit that provides life support, so it's not so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:08.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,May I make a suggestion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:11.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What is it, Sano-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:18.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Kamogawa Asumi leave the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:18.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I believe that it would be best to make
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:20.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,S-Sano-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:22.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What are you saying all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:29.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Kamogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:55.74,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,Back then, it would've been better\NIf I'd just had a little courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:06.21,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,If I was still my weak self, I wouldn't have awoken to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:13.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,little one, I'll tell you something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:16.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Something interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:16.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:24.39,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,When you're in the water and you look ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.90,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,You can see the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:46.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Marika-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:48.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Hey hold on to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:57.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Really... you dummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:05.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Marika-chan, you came to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:12.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I wonder if I would be able to save you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:16.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I have to get much, much stronger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:21.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I have to get stronger so I can\Ndo more things without falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:26.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Here, dry yourself off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:28.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Do you have a change of clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:29.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:37.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,To begin with, this budget is within expected\Nboundaries, except in Kamogawa's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:42.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,In this case, wouldn't having her leave be the best answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:46.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Don't say stupid things! There's no way we can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:50.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It will become the responsibility of\Nthe school that admitted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:56.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,If we have her leave of her own accord,\Nthere would be no problem, would there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:01.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,So that's what he meant by it being simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:08.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It is the first year for the {space}astronaut course,\Nso we have a rather large number of students...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:11.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,...but next year will only have ten students overall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:16.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,size of space suit will be needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:16.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,In this case, it is unlikely that this
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:25.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,is the only one under 160 cm of height.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:25.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,looking at our students now, Kamogawa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:29.56,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Her academic performance is only slightly above average.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:32.39,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Even it she continues training...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:37.06,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,the chances of her distinguishing herself from the other\Nstudents and being able to go to space are exceedingly low.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:39.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,To use this much money for such a student—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:41.49,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:47.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Are body size and grades that important for going to space?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:51.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,That would be no different than the\Ntraining we've had up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:55.83,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Having a student leave because of the school s\Nfinancial circumstances is out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:21:01.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Getting ordinary children to try and become\Nastronauts as a natural goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:07.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Having space be a more accessible thing\Nthat is closer to people's lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:12.02,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Are these not what the Space School is trying to accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:27.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's just as Shiomi-sensei says.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:32.83,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The budget will be very tight, but\Nit's for the future of this student.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:36.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Let us all cooperate and pull through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:41.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Shiomi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:44.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Hm? Do you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:48.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I heard that you pushed for the\Nadmission of Kamogawa Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:52.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Why do you back that particular student so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:57.19,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,It's her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:03.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,She has the eyes that you've lost. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:20.92,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,Since I was small, it's always been my\Ndream to become an {space}astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:28.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,My friends from long ago used to talk\Nabout space with eyes like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.77,0:22:35.35,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Sano-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.69,0:22:45.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Try not to make things difficult. Just stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.24,0:22:49.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What you just said, about one's own accord...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.18,0:24:36.80,Spica - Title,,0,0,90,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.51,0:24:36.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Sano-sensei's words pierced my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.81,0:24:40.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,He said there's no way that I'd be\Nchosen to become an astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.81,0:24:41.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.89,0:24:45.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What does he mean, just because I m\NKamogawa Tomorou's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.98,0:24:50.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It even gets Kei-chan angry. I return to Yuigahama alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.74,0:24:53.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I don't know what to do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.24,0:24:57.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Next time on Twin Spica. Wounded Wings.